# AurusAI — Frontend Cursor Prompt

Use this file for all frontend work on AurusAI.

## What You Are Building

AurusAI is a personal gold trading intelligence dashboard for an experienced XAU/USD intraday trader.

This is NOT a marketing site. NOT a SaaS landing page. NOT a generic fintech UI.

It is a live trading tool — opened every morning before the London session, kept visible during trades, checked on mobile for alerts. Every design decision must serve that use case.

The aesthetic direction is: **Bloomberg Terminal meets premium dark trading platform**. Dense, data-rich, fast, zero decoration. Think professional-grade instrument, not consumer app.

---

## Typography

**Primary font:** IBM Plex Mono — all data, numbers, prices, times, labels, badges, tickers  
**Secondary font:** IBM Plex Sans — body text, descriptions, AI commentary, notes

Import in index.html or main CSS:

```html
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

**Never use:** Inter, Roboto, Arial, system-ui, or any generic sans-serif for this project.

Typography rules:

- All prices: IBM Plex Mono, minimum 12px, always 2 decimal places
- All labels: IBM Plex Mono, 9px, uppercase, letter-spacing: 2px
- All AI-generated text: IBM Plex Sans, 11px, line-height 1.5
- Section headers in panels: IBM Plex Mono, 9px, uppercase, letter-spacing: 2px, color: var(--text3)

---

## Color System

Use CSS variables. Never hardcode hex values outside of :root.

```css
:root {
  --bg:        #080808;   /* Page background */
  --bg1:       #0F0F0F;   /* Panel background */
  --bg2:       #141414;   /* Inner panel, cards */
  --bg3:       #1A1A1A;   /* Hover states, inputs */
  --border:    #242424;   /* Default borders */
  --border2:   #2E2E2E;   /* Subtle borders */
  --gold:      #C9A84C;   /* Primary accent — XAU/gold branding */
  --gold2:     #E8C97A;   /* Price display, highlights */
  --gold-dim:  #6B5520;   /* Muted gold, borders */
  --text:      #E2D9C8;   /* Primary text */
  --text2:     #8A8070;   /* Secondary text */
  --text3:     #504840;   /* Muted labels */
  --green:     #2ECC71;   /* Win, bullish, up, active */
  --red:       #E74C3C;   /* Loss, bearish, down, HIGH impact */
  --amber:     #F39C12;   /* Warning, MEDIUM impact, neutral bias */
  --blue:      #3498DB;   /* Info, links */
}
```

**Impact color rules** (apply consistently everywhere):

- HIGH impact → var(--red)
- MEDIUM impact → var(--amber)
- LOW impact → var(--green)

**Trade direction colors:**

- LONG → var(--green)
- SHORT → var(--red)

**Trade outcome colors:**

- Win → var(--green)
- Loss → var(--red)
- Breakeven → var(--amber)
- Open → var(--blue)

