## Layout Architecture

### App Shell

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Topbar (44px)  — price · session · next event · time │
├────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│    │                                                  │
│ S  │              Page Content                        │
│ i  │              (scrollable)                        │
│ d  │                                                  │
│ e  │                                                  │
│    │                                                  │
├────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Status Bar (24px) — service health indicators        │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Sidebar

- Width: 52px, fixed, never collapses on desktop
- Background: var(--bg1), border-right: 1px solid var(--border)
- Logo: "AURUS" in IBM Plex Mono, 11px, gold, vertical writing-mode, rotated 180deg
- Nav icons: 36×36px, border-radius 6px, icon-only (no labels)
- Active state: color var(--gold), background rgba(201,168,76,0.12), border 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2)
- Hover state: color var(--gold), background rgba(201,168,76,0.08)

### Topbar (44px)

Sections separated by vertical 1px borders. Left to right:

1. XAU/USD price + 24h change badge
2. Session indicator (London Open / New York / Asian / Closed)
3. Next high-impact event + time in WAT
4. Session bias (from morning brief)
5. Live WAT clock (updates every second)

**Session badge variants:**

- London active: gold text, rgba(201,168,76,0.12) background
- NY active: green text, rgba(46,204,113,0.1) background
- Closed: var(--text3), var(--bg3) background

### Status Bar (24px)

Bottom strip showing backend service health:

- Price Feed, News Monitor, Level Watcher, Scheduler
- Green dot (animated pulse) = active, grey dot = inactive
- Right side: "AurusAI v1.0 · Personal Build"

