## Panel System

All content lives inside panels. Panels have a consistent structure:

```jsx
<div className="panel">
  <div className="panel-header">
    <span className="panel-title">PANEL NAME</span>
    <span className="panel-badge">metadata</span>
  </div>
  <div className="panel-body">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

**Panel CSS:**

```css
.panel {
  background: var(--bg1);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.panel-header {
  height: 32px;
  padding: 0 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--bg2);
}
.panel-title {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
```

