## First Build Instruction for Cursor

When starting, say:

**"Build the AppShell first — Sidebar, Topbar, and StatusBar with all CSS variables and fonts configured. Use placeholder content for the topbar data. Then build the Dashboard page with all panels using static mock data. Connect to real API endpoints only after the UI is complete and approved."**

Build UI with static data first. Wire to backend second. This prevents getting blocked on API issues while building the interface.

